Plus, you make good money, so there's really no excuse.
而且你赚得不少，所以真的没什么借口。

95
00:04:15,440 --> 00:04:17,440
It's just simply because you're a mama's boy.
纯粹是因为你是个妈宝男。

96
00:04:17,440 --> 00:04:18,440
Whatever, dude.
随便你怎么说，哥们。

97
00:04:18,440 --> 00:04:19,880
I have everything I need.
我需要的东西都有。

98
00:04:19,880 --> 00:04:20,880
Why would I move out?
我为什么要搬出去？

99
00:04:20,880 --> 00:04:22,640
I have a great roof over my head.
我有个好住处。

100
