还有一个口语短语用来描述这个男人，就是“mama's boy”。

130
00:05:47,720 --> 00:05:50,640
He says, his friend says he's a mama's boy.
他说，他朋友说他是妈宝男。

131
00:05:50,640 --> 00:05:51,640
Mama's boy.
妈宝男。

132
00:05:51,640 --> 00:05:53,560
So mama is mother.
所以“mama”是妈妈。

133
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:57,560
Mama's boy means that he's very, very close with his mother.
“Mama's boy”意思是他跟妈妈非常非常亲近。

134
00:05:57,560 --> 00:05:59,800
This is not a good thing to say.
这不是什么好话。

135
00:05:59,800 --> 00:06:01,640
It's usually something that's a little bit critical.
通常有点批评意味。

136
00:06:01,640 --> 00:06:02,640
Okay.
好的。

137
00:06:02,640 --> 00:06:03,640
So say he's a mama's boy.
所以就说他是妈宝男。

138
00:06:03,640 --> 00:06:04,640
Okay.
好的。

139
00:06:04,640 --> 00:06:09,520
So his mother washes his clothes, she cooks his food, she does everything for him.
所以他妈妈给他洗衣服、做饭，什么都替他做。

140
00:06:09,520 --> 00:06:10,520
Right.
对。

141
00:06:10,520 --> 00:06:12,000
And he doesn't do anything for himself.
他自己什么都不做。

142
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:13,000
He's like a little baby.
他就像个小宝宝。

143
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:16,840
He's like a child and his mama, his mother does everything for him.
他像个孩子，他妈妈什么都替他做。

144
00:06:16,840 --> 00:06:19,240
So it is a little bit like an insult, I guess.
所以这有点像侮辱，我想。

145
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:20,240
Yes.
是的。

146
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:21,240
Okay.
好的。

147
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:24,720
So it's not really a good thing to call someone a mama's boy unless in this situation, they're
所以叫别人妈宝男不是什么好事，除非在这种情况下，他们是

148
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:26,760
friends and his friend is saying, well, you know what?
朋友，他朋友在说，嗯，你知道吗？

149
00:06:26,760 --> 00:06:28,600
It seems like you're a mama's boy.
看起来你是个妈宝男。

150
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:29,600
Exactly.
正是。

151
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:30,600
All right.
好的。

152
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:36,120
So our next phrase is when he was justifying and say, why would I move out?
下一个短语是他辩解时说，我为什么要搬出去？

153
