00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:32,160
the economy.
不景气的时候。

198
00:08:32,160 --> 00:08:34,440
Yeah, but you're almost 40.
是啊，但你都快40岁了。

199
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:37,920
Plus, you make good money, so there's really no excuse.
而且你收入不错，所以真的没什么借口。

200
00:08:37,920 --> 00:08:39,960
It's just simply because you're a mama's boy.
这纯粹是因为你是个妈宝男。

201
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:40,960
Whatever, dude.
随便你怎么说，哥们。

202
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:42,360
I have everything I need.
我什么都不缺。

203
00:08:42,360 --> 00:08:43,740
Why would I move out?
我为什么要搬出去？

204
00:08:43,740 --> 00:08:45,120
Have a great roof over my head.
我有个很好的遮风挡雨的屋顶。

205
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:47,100
My mom does my laundry and cooks for me.
我妈妈帮我洗衣服、做饭。

206
00:08:47,100 --> 00:08:49,000
